  "content": [
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "He hasn't spoken about his personal religious views, but given that he's a Spaniard, it's highly likely that he, or at least his family, has something to do with the Catholic tradition."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "There's a chance Villa is a bit intolerant of at least one religion. Villa was party to an international controversy when, during a game, Villa and opponent Mesut Ozil got into a brawl. Ozil said of the incident:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.allvoices.com/contributed-news/10028659-did-david-villa-insulted-mesut-ozils-islam-religion-at-super-cup-brawl",
      "sourceTitle": "Did David Villa insulted Mesut Ozil's Islam religion at Super Cup brawl?",
      "text": "I did this because I was defending my religion because David Villa insulted Islam."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "Unfortunately, that seems to be the extent of Villa's public commentary on religion."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "text": "Son of a miner's politics"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.davidvilla7.es/en/biography/",
      "sourceTitle": "David Villa Official Website: Biography.",
      "text": "Villa's politics are relatively minimal as well. He has sided with \"labor\" in the seemingly endless austerity strikes plaguing Spain. Villa's father was a miner"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.totalbarca.com/2012/news/villa-supports-spanish-miners/",
      "sourceTitle": "Villa supports Spanish miners",
      "text": "and when coal miners marched in Madrid–fearing for their jobs–Villa expressed his support."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "Other than that, no official political stances from the Villa camp that I can find. Let us know if anything changes."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    }
  ],
